---
title: Projects
stylesheets:
- projects
---
{{#> default}}
<main class="projects view">
  <section class="projects-intro">
    <h4>Projects</h4>
    <p>
      A list of stuff I've worked on and contributed to till date. I personally attempt to use a different set of technologies for each individual project. Each new project presents the opportunity to push limits creatively and technically.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="project-articles">
    <ul class="articles-list">
      {{#each projects as |p _|}}
      <li class="radius project">
        <i>{{> link text=p.name url=p.url class="project-url"}}</i>
        <p>{{p.text}}<br/><i>{{p.tech}}</i> ({{p.year}})</p>
      </li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </section>
</main>
{{/default}}
